title: Prana Bar Natural
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Beer/Wine, Argentinian
description: Vegetarian restaurant in a small town dominated by steak, pizza, and pasta places. Sits in the center of the city on the main avenue. In addition to a daily menu, it offers many kinds of food: sweet and savory crepes, soup, curry vegetables, pasta, desserts, juices, and local beer. Staff is aware of what vegan means, so ask. A chess game is there for guests to play. Relaxed atmosphere.
